118
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,639
not everyone will only compliment you.

119
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:45,240
They'll also choose who to compliment.

120
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:47,199
But with me sitting here,

121
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,560
