150
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,560
Are you for real?

151
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,959
Really, look.

152
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,079
I want to criticize

153
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,000
